The paper deals with video segmentation using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of structured prediction and weakly annotated data, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with motion information in videos, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of the proposed method in robotics (cs.RO).
